{"tid":1753582,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"15歲學生攜帶雷射筆,裁定管有攻擊性武器罪成","createTime":"2019-11-25T03:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T05:13:31.000Z","uid":118842,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f2a36d94ab94c36a5969e812733884b979d313d4","tid":1753582,"uid":118842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:29:09.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】一名15歲中學生因攜帶雷射筆，被裁定管有攻擊性武器罪成，被判入更生中心。<br />\n<br />\n涉案學生9月21日，在屯門站附被發現攜有一枝雷射筆及經改裝的長傘及行山杖等。辯方求情指，被告被捕後還柙至今，希望判處可即時獲釋的刑期，以繼續學業，但裁判官認為更生中心提供有系統訓練，相信有助被告改過自身，加強守法意識，又指年輕人可以有自己意見，但必須以合法方式表達，於示威或集會中持有攻擊性武器，可威脅前線執法人員安全及社會秩序，亦妨礙其他人和平表達訴求的權利。裁判官拒絕辯方保釋，等候上訴申請。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=371139&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D371139%26refer%3D&d=dTdn096UhK%2BcydR5vLM29258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=713e5b95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D371139%26refer%3D&h=526c0acf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=371139&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"d2fda266be275579c479888e86a0174bb63579d9","tid":1753582,"uid":304321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:30:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我屌你老母 佢得15歲ja!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"5a3decd16a11ea0e8341cd3c467725578c225a0f","tid":1753582,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:31:09.000Z","msg":"必須守法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42ccad415de246da4f35753176129cdfd2af274","tid":1753582,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:32:01.000Z","msg":"屌你老母咁撚樣都砌得入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\